      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibabas-lingxi-games-says-management-step-down-make-way-younger-execs-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份内部备忘录显示，阿里巴巴集团旗下视频游戏部门灵犀游戏已告知员工，其领导团队将辞职，为更年轻的管理层让路。]]></description>
